headline: Bonds and Stocks Are Moving In a Way Not Seen in Months
summary: The U.S. government bond market is failing to provide shelter for investors away from falling stocks. A popular Treasury exchange-traded fund, the iShares 20+ Year Treasury Bond known by its ticker TLT, is down 1.

headline: Zacks.com featured highlights include Dredge & Dock, StoneCo, PG&E and EnerSys
summary: GLDD, STNE, PCG and ENS stand out as low P/CF value plays as rate-cut optimism lifts markets and boosts interest in cash-flow strength.
